{"name":"Crown of Communing","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/crown-gold-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>This crown is platinum inlaid with obsidian, and and is used to commune with the spirits of the dead. While wearing it you may cast <em>speak with dead</em> (one charge), <em>commune with dead</em> (two charges) or <em>deathvision</em> (three charges).</p><p>The crown has three charges. It regains 1d3 expended charges daily at dawn.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CSI Waterdeep","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"3","per":"day","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":2,"2YnGkU1l5ZNW8ikj":3},"flags":{"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wcEVWLDif9wrZcNY"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1669086115931,"modifiedTime":1676826564824,"lastModifiedBy":"2YnGkU1l5ZNW8ikj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"CEY1VTrDyM6bV76g"}
{"name":"Commune with Dead (Crown)","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/undead-ghost-scream-teal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can commune with the soul of the creature whose dead body (or part thereof) you touch. The spell fails if it has been used on this soul within the last 10 days.</p><p class=\"western\">Until the spell ends you can ask the soul up to five questions. The soul knows only what it knew in life; as this is soul-to-soul contact, language is not a barrier. Answers are usually brief, cryptic, and repetitive, and the soul is under no compulsion to offer a truthful answer if you are hostile to it or it recognizes you as an enemy. The soul can't learn new information, doesn't comprehend anything that has happened since it died, and can't speculate about future events.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"10","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"charges","target":"","amount":2},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":5,"school":"nec","components":{"vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":true},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"2YnGkU1l5ZNW8ikj":3},"flags":{"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"midiProperties":{"nodam":false,"fulldam":false,"halfdam":false,"rollOther":false,"critOther":false,"magicdam":false,"magiceffect":false,"concentration":false,"toggleEffect":false,"ignoreTotalCover":false,"autoFailFriendly":false,"aut