{"name":"Speak with Dead (Crown)","ownership":{"default":0,"GipOrFkJloqZuOfJ":3,"2YnGkU1l5ZNW8ikj":3},"type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You grant the semblance of life and intelligence to a corpse of your choice within range, allowing it to answer the questions you pose. The corpse must still have a mouth and can't be undead. The spell fails if the corpse was the target of this spell within the last 10 days.</p><p>Until the spell ends, you can ask the corpse up to five questions. The corpse knows only what it knew in life, including the languages it knew. Answers are usually brief, cryptic, or repetitive, and the corpse is under no compulsion to offer a truthful answer if you are hostile to it or it recognizes you as an enemy. This spell doesn't return the creature's soul to its body, only its animating spirit. Thus, the corpse can't learn new information, doesn't comprehend anything that has happened since it died, and can't speculate about future events.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 277","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"10","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"charges","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"nec","components":{"vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"Burning incense","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":true},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.spells.I2LUSF5ogc7Bj62e"},"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"midiProperties":{"nodam":false,"fulldam":false,"halfdam":false,"rollOther":false,"critOther":false,"magicdam":false,"magiceffect":false,"concentration":false,"toggleEffect":false,"ignoreTotalCover":false,"autoFailFriendly":false,"autoSaveFriendly":false,"offHandWeapon":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-shadow-monster-green.webp","effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1661787234108,"modifiedTime":1676826578367,"lastModifiedBy":"2YnGkU1l5ZNW8ikj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"cxJT6oc8NrrtWE5M"}
{"name":"Deathvision (Crown)","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/skull-humanoid-white-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You experience the last minute of the life of the creature whose dead body (or part thereof) you touch, through its eyes, ears and sense of touch. This spell fails if it has been used on the body within the last 10 days.</p><p class=\"western\">If you spend the full minute concentrating on the vision you will experience the death of the target. Roll a DC 15 Charisma check. On failure you will suffer 3d6 psychic damage.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"charges","target":"qOvQOCIU4aslpd3G","amount":3},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":7,"school":"nec","components":{"vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":true},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"2YnGkU1l5ZNW8ikj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Vq7JJW4usnvHrvDY"},"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"midiProperties":{"nodam":false,"fulldam":false,"halfdam":false,"rollOther":false,"critOther":false,"magicdam":false,"magiceffect":false,"concentration":false,"toggleEffect":false,"ignoreTotalCover":false,"autoFailFriendly":false,"autoSaveFriendly":false,"offHandWeapon":false}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1669086854901,"modifiedTime":1676826575144,"lastModif